    "description": "只有两个按钮能让你的羽毛屁股跳起来，死亡是不可避免的。<br>&quot;鸭子的绝望》是一款疯狂的高难度平台游戏，由一个荒诞的故事驱动，让你享受痛苦。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/74821023d4c5c26364b59bdbac6c88cb.poster.avif?t=1717841986\" width=530 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/74821023d4c5c26364b59bdbac6c88cb.webm?t=1717841986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/74821023d4c5c26364b59bdbac6c88cb.mp4?t=1717841986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><br></li><li>残疾弹跳鸭的游戏玩法。<br></li><li>关卡设计和机制都考虑到了快速运行。<br></li><li>老玩家可收集彩蛋和解锁奖牌。<br></li><li>讽刺故事中的疯狂角色，充满史诗般的曲折。<br></li><li>血与泪。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/6580a647bf1e4eddbc27d13b2083ade5.poster.avif?t=1717841986\" width=524 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/6580a647bf1e4eddbc27d13b2083ade5.webm?t=1717841986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/6580a647bf1e4eddbc27d13b2083ade5.mp4?t=1717841986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >狂热冒险</h2><br>当你的朋友们都去海边大快朵颐时，你却被困在臭气熏天的粉红古城。被闪电击中后无法飞行，你选择了痛苦较少的办法：结束这一切...... 但就在你做出无法挽回的决定时，一个地精从虚空中出现，让你永生！你现在唯一的选择是：寻找金羽毛，希望有朝一日能飞向梦想！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/5e4caa4cbcce0222f9202028031a7a56.poster.avif?t=1717841986\" width=524 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/5e4caa4cbcce0222f9202028031a7a56.webm?t=1717841986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404430/extras/5e4caa4cbcce0222f9202028031a7a56.mp4?t=1717841986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br>你唯一的移动方式是什么？像小鸡一样跳跃，像橡皮球一样弹跳！揭开这些机制的神秘面纱，它们易学得令人发指，却又<i>难以掌握</i>。只有鲜血、汗水和泪水，才能带你闯过难度不断增加的 72 个手工制作的关卡！还不累？尝试获取所有彩蛋，并在每个关卡中创造最佳成绩。<br><br>跳进荒诞的旅程中，在地狱和天堂之间翩翩起舞，实现成为真正烤鸭的梦想！",
